description: Never leave Cursor attribution or AI trailers in git commits or PRs
alwaysApply: true
---

# No Cursor trace

When creating commits or pull requests:

- Do **not** add `Co-authored-by`, `Made-with`, `Generated-by`, or any Cursor/AI attribution trailers
- Do **not** mention Cursor, Copilot, or AI assistants in commit messages or PR bodies
- Write commit messages and PR text as a normal human contributor would
- Keep authorship as the local git user only; never rewrite author/committer to an AI identity
